"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## [Perspective: Bitcoin is not boring](https://blog.coinbase.com/perspective-bitcoin-is-not-boring-ee62de4d23e7?source=user_profile---------3-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*0TJnDCSywXGPgubt0zcNcg.png)](https://blog.coinbase.com/perspective-bitcoin-is-not-boring-ee62de4d23e7?source=user_profile---------3-------------------------------)\\n\\nBy [Mark Nesbitt](https://medium.com/@mwnesbitt)\\n\\n*Crypto is a rapidly growing space, with many views on how it might evolve. This series explores various ideas on crypto’s future and does not necessarily reflect the view of Coinbase.*\\n\\n**TLDR: This post explores a typical evolution of understanding Bitcoin, how its most common criticisms can…**\\n\\n## [Incident Post Mortem: November 23, 2021](https://blog.coinbase.com/incident-post-mortem-november-23-2021-d507821b8459?source=user_profile---------4-------------------------------)\\n\\n**Summary**\\n\\nBetween 4:00 pm and approximately 5:36 pm PT on Tuesday, November 23rd, we experienced an outage across most Coinbase production systems. During this outage, users were unable to access Coinbase using our websites and apps, and therefore were unable to use our products. …\\n\\n## [Coinbase Community Analyst Program](https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-community-analyst-program-2f297c70cda0?source=user_profile---------5-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*mSEMctUi-iIX0R7Q5-RpSg.png)](https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-community-analyst-program-2f297c70cda0?source=user_profile---------5-------------------------------)\\n\\nCoinbase is delighted to announce the launch of the Community Analyst Program, a.k.a. the CAP Program. This is a new and exciting way for students, professionals and community members who share our core beliefs to contribute to Coinbase’s mission to increase economic freedom.\\n\\nIf you are crypto-native, crypto-passionate or insatiably…\\n\\n## [Scaling Content at Coinbase](https://blog.coinbase.com/scaling-content-at-coinbase-df75ff3208d4?source=user_profile---------6-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*70Mh-\\\\_Ao0-ftKN-8)](https://blog.coinbase.com/scaling-content-at-coinbase-df75ff3208d4?source=user_profile---------6-------------------------------)\\n\\n*By Clay Kohut, Senior Software Engineer*\\n\\n**TLDR: Over the past year, Coinbase has invested in tooling to eliminate static content across our web frontend. This is the story of how we did it and why it’s important.**\\n\\n## Coinbase Learn(ed)\\n\\nThe Coinbase educational portal, [Coinbase Learn](https://coinbase.com/learn), launched in late 2020. Learn contains *hundreds…*\\n\\n## [Coinbase Transparency Report -Q1-Q3, 2021](https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-transparency-report-q1-q3-2021-80bb5c785da?source=user_profile---------8-------------------------------)\\n\\n*By Paul Grewal, Chief Legal Officer*\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*5gt3zU3RijpyerBV.png)](https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-transparency-report-q1-q3-2021-80bb5c785da?source=user_profile---------8-------------------------------)\\n\\nCoinbase is proud to publish our third Transparency Report. This report covers the period between January 1 through September 30, 2021\\\\*. As Coinbase continues to grow and offer services in new markets, the number of legitimate information requests we receive from law enforcement agencies…\\n\\n## [Decentralized Social (DESO) is launching on Coinbase](https://blog.coinbase.com/decentralized-social-deso-is-launching-on-coinbase-c17ee3613f90?source=user_profile---------9-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*EsThLGRaxhILgBkJ)](https://blog.coinbase.com/decentralized-social-deso-is-launching-on-coinbase-c17ee3613f90?source=user_profile---------9-------------------------------)\\n\\nStarting today** Decentralized Social (DESO) is** available on Coinbase.com and in the Coinbase Android and iOS apps. Coinbase customers can now trade, send, receive, or store ***DESO ***in most Coinbase-supported regions, with certain exceptions indicated in each asset page [here](https://help.coinbase.com/en/coinbase/supported-crypto). Trading for these assets is also supported on Coinbase Pro.\\n\\n[**…**](https://www.deso.org/)\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640875070,\"title\":\"Coinbase – Medium\"},\"digest\":\"70JWdnE5EGqHW9YXfJ_MLnmD75hXsYaoHkeb9okzQ4c\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xcd9D9D81899bDf1ec8acc612E411d159DbA12d2F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"HsrtfPyJL5gU3cJmmxuCm4Uqizv42rfxvNl4B07FQjM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"wtgVxHJzzePOfeZhkVhV4P2RCBqDwYI-6WUuoMbvrDE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"EXcNJk2dWitUsazXeHzoUQn6toNxsoLPbsAsZcUt32ufU3TpkosmFXOzqQI0lVkyLuvjFWQu8QD4BDLwnC4w-g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x125906394c147676ec24a0333c156efb0b248a0a395d1377bade3805996b1da2288693d841932c9dd29e5960ff51831daa6d120b4012f0690a4a63366dd546ff1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"HsrtfPyJL5gU3cJmmxuCm4Uqizv42rfxvNl4B07FQjM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"wtgVxHJzzePOfeZhkVhV4P2RCBqDwYI-6WUuoMbvrDE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"70JWdnE5EGqHW9YXfJ_MLnmD75hXsYaoHkeb9okzQ4c\"}"